"title": "1611: Scripture, inspiration and authority of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1611",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Those writings that are acknowledged to be the word of God to be revered as issuing from him and as having his authority.</p>\n<h2>Recognition of a body of sacred writings</h2>\n<h3>In the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:1\">NEH 8:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:7\">EXO 24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:34\">JOS 8:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:8\">2KI 22:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:14\">2CH 34:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:2\">2KI 23:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:30\">2CH 34:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:12\">2CH 35:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:18\">EZR 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:8\">NEH 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:3\">NEH 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:1\">NEH 13:1</a></p>\n<h3>By Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:29\">MAT 22:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:21\">LUK 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:27\">LUK 24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:45\">LUK 24:45</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:13\">MAT 21:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:46\">LUK 19:46</a> <em>Jesus Christ frequently appealed to the OT as a recognised sacred corpus, with the expression “it is written”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:7\">ISA 56:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:11\">JER 7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:4\">LUK 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:7\">MAT 4:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:12\">LUK 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:16\">DEU 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:10\">MAT 4:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:8\">LUK 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:13\">DEU 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:42\">MAT 21:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:10\">MRK 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22-Ps118:23\">PSA 118:22–118:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:31\">MAT 26:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:27\">MRK 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:7\">ZEC 13:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6-Mark7:7\">MRK 7:6–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:27\">LUK 7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:1\">MAL 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:38\">JHN 7:38</a></p>\n<h3>By the apostles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14-2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:14–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:15-Acts1:17\">ACT 1:15–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1-Rom1:2\">ROM 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:4\">1CO 15:3–15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>By the early church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:11\">ACT 17:11</a></p>\n<h2>The inspiration of Scripture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13-2Kgs17:14\">2KI 17:13–17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:43-Matt22:44\">MAT 22:43–22:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:36\">MRK 12:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:2\">HEB 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:10-1Pet1:11\">1PE 1:10–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:20-2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:20–1:21</a></p>\n<h2>The authority of Scripture recognised in the OT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:89\">PSA 119:89</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:6\">JOS 23:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8\">JOS 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:11\">2KI 22:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:1-Ezra10:4\">EZR 10:1–10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:9-Ezra10:12\">EZR 10:9–10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:1-Neh13:3\">NEH 13:1–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:8\">ISA 40:8</a></p>\n<h2>The authority of Scripture recognised in the NT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:34-John10:36\">JHN 10:34–10:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:17-Matt5:19\">MAT 5:17–5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:21-Luke21:23\">LUK 21:21–21:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:17\">LUK 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">1TH 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ claims scriptural authority for his own words</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:34-Matt24:35\">MAT 24:34–24:35</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:30-Mark13:31\">MRK 13:30–13:31</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:47-John12:50\">JHN 12:47–12:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10\">JHN 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23-John14:24\">JHN 14:23–14:24</a></p>",
